games.comment: Hakeem Nicks had only 1 reception each for 43 and 54 yards, respectively. Nicks, who was seeing his first action since his Week 1 injury, was able to score a touchdown on that catch. He'll continue to evolve into a dangerous weapon for Manning.    The Giants also abused the Chiefs on the ground with
Hakeem Nicks, who paced the team with 9 catches for 72 yards. No other Colt registered more than 37 receiving yards.
